OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson taken unwell before
OL,4,Ckick-off at Old Trafford
OL,6,FThere are reports that Sir Alex
OL,7,FFerguson left Old Trafford ahead of
OL,8,FManchester United's Premier League
OL,9,Fclash with Liverpool after feeling
OL,10,Funwell, just over an hour before kick-
OL,11,Foff.
OL,13,FThe 84-year-old was treated at the
OL,14,Fstadium by medics.
OL,16,FIt is understood it isn't being
OL,17,Ftreated as an emergency and was
OL,18,Finstead a precaution.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
