OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777878261
OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson taken unwell before
OL,4,Ckick-off at Old Trafford
OL,6,FSir Alex is a regular at Old Trafford
OL,7,Fand was posing for photographs with
OL,8,Fsupporters before he began to feel
OL,9,Funwell and was treated at the scene
OL,10,Fbefore leaving the ground.
OL,12,FThere were conflicting reports about
OL,13,Fthe nature of his treatment, with some
OL,14,Fsuggesting he was checked in an
OL,15,Fambulance on site and others saying he
OL,16,Fwas taken to hospital.
OL,18,FUnited have been contacted for comment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
