FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777878261
OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson taken unwell before
OL,4,Ckick-off at Old Trafford
OL,6,FThe former Manchester United manager
OL,7,Fhad a health scare in 2018 when he
OL,8,Fsuffered a brain haemorrhage and
OL,9,Fneeded life-saving surgery.
OL,11,FThere is nothing to suggest today's
OL,12,Fincident is related to that.
OL,14,FFerguson is a regular at home games
OL,15,Fand has a row of seats in the Old
OL,16,FTrafford directors' box.
OL,18,FThe Scot was a club ambassador for 12
OL,19,Fyears after his retirement from
OL,20,Fmanagement in 2013.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
